short-description: Ditch the boring and overstated factory chrome front grilles and get a darker and more aggressive look on your car. These replacement grilles are made from ABS plastic with a carbon fiber weave on the exterior frame. Carbon fiber is replacing chrome and aluminum as the most desired decorative trim. Since it has its roots in aerospace and motorsports the look gives off the impression of cutting-edge technology and lightness. But our suppliers have improved the fit and finish of carbon’s inherently rough appearance. There are several quality grades to carbon fiber weave and we would put this right in the middle. It’s a good quality carbon weave without costing hundreds more like an Original BMW carbon part would. We inspect each grille for finish imperfections and quality issues so you’re getting only the ones we approve. If you want to complete the carbon fiber makeover on your car check out our other carbon grilles, emblems, trim, and spoilers. But please note that we source our carbon products from multiple suppliers and the carbon pattern will vary. Our grilles are sold in pairs – one for the left and one for the right. Installation is easy as they snap out and then snap back in.     2007-3/2010    - 328i, 328xi, 335i & 335xi (pre-LCI, non-facelift models)  2007-3/2010    328i & 335i (pre-LCI, non-facelift models)  2008+    (fits M3 coupe, M3 sedan & M3 convertible)

cleanDesc: Carbon Fiber Double Slat Center Grills - F12/F13/F06 640i, 650i, M6 ...
short-description: Ditch the boring and overstated factory chrome front grilles and get a darker and more aggressive look on your car. Only the M6 came with the double-slat grilles so these are a way to add some M6 flair to the standard 640/650 front end. These also replace the stock M6 grilles too to add some carbon fiber accents. These replacement grilles are made from ABS plastic with a carbon fiber weave on the exterior frame. Carbon fiber is replacing chrome and aluminum as the most desired decorative trim. Since it has its roots in aerospace and motorsports the look gives off the impression of cutting-edge technology and lightness. But our suppliers have improved the fit and finish of carbon’s inherently rough appearance. There are several quality grades to carbon fiber weave and we would put this right in the middle. It’s a good quality carbon weave without costing hundreds more like an Original BMW carbon part would. We inspect each grille for finish imperfections and quality issues so you’re getting only the ones we approve. If you want to complete the carbon fiber makeover on your car check out our other carbon grilles, emblems, trim, and spoilers. But please note that we source our carbon products from multiple suppliers and the carbon pattern will vary. Our grilles are sold in pairs – one for the left and one for the right. Installation is easy as they snap out and then snap back in.     2012+    640i 650i 650i xDrive M6   2013+    640i Gran Coupe 650i Gran Coupe 650i xDrive Gran Coupe M6 Gran Coupe

        ...
short-description: Directly swap out the OEM front chrome grille surrounds on the F97 X3M and F98 X4M with the AutoTecknic's signature prestige dry carbon grille surrounds without having to purchase another complete set of grilles. Developed and engineered with the OEM standard as the framework, these AutoTecknic replacement dry carbon grille surrounds are made with 100% pre-preg carbon fiber that results in overall durable construction with strong clips and tabs for a secure and seamless fit. Dry carbon fiber's name comes from its manufacturing process. Dry carbon fiber is formed by using a "pre-preg" or impregnated piece of carbon materials. This piece of carbon is first placed into a mold, and then into a sealed vacuum (autoclave) to properly cure. This particular method creates the least amount of waste and forms a lighter version of carbon than the “wet” method. The autoclave vacuuming process of making dry carbon means that there are fewer pinholes and virtually no air pockets that form in the carbon. Dry carbon is the highest-quality version of carbon fiber products that are produced. Package includes one pair of passenger and driver side direct OEM replacement dry carbon fiber grille surrounds for theF97 X3M and F98 X4M

cleanDesc: Black Fender Side Grill Set - F10 M5
short-description: We love our F10 M5 project car, but from the moment we first laid eyes on it at the BMW Welt European Delivery Center in Munich, we KNEW the ugly chrome fenders grills had to go. They are out of place, and the chrome overshadows an otherwise "nice" touch on the F10 chassis M5. And we knew we weren't the only ones who thought that.      Fortunately, we now have the solution! These matte black M5 fender grills are a direct replacement to the standard grills, are easy to install and make dramatic visual improvement over the stock chrome grills. Check out the before and after effect on our Project F10 M5, you can see for yourself how much cleaner the side profile looks. In our opinion, these are the grills every F10 M5 should have left the factory with. The matte black finish looks wonderful with any color -- light or dark. Whether your M5 is bone stock, or destined for many upgrades and modifications, these grills are simply a no brainer.        2012+      M5
